247
00:23:43.250 --> 00:23:44.770
I know what it is.

248
00:23:44.890 --> 00:23:48.050
I love H.J. so terribly, but...

249
00:23:50.250 --> 00:23:53.050
...he isn't always awfully nice
to me.


250
00:23:54.250 --> 00:23:56.970
- It's just so difficult for me
to trust anyone.


251
00:23:57.130 --> 00:24:00.330
- Well, naturally, with the life you've led
and your marriage.


252
00:24:00.450 --> 00:24:03.770
- I didn't mean my marriage.
Not Stephan.


253
00:24:03.930 --> 00:24:06.970
- Y-you mustn't think
I don't see the...


254
00:24:07.090 --> 00:24:09.650
the angle that you look
at life from.


255
00:24:10.490 --> 00:24:11.690
Because I do.

256
00:24:13.570 --> 00:24:14.690
Please rest now.

257
00:24:15.650 --> 00:24:18.530
Do rest.
Don't let's talk anymore.


258
00:24:21.610 --> 00:24:25.290
- It really wasn't any use
talking to Lois about Stephan,


259
00:24:25.450 --> 00:24:27.610
