399
00:36:53.570 --> 00:36:56.170
- They're like members of a harem
who can't get on.


400
00:37:03.130 --> 00:37:05.130
- It'll all blow over, no doubt.

401
00:37:05.610 --> 00:37:08.810
- He doesn't know himself.
That's what's so frightening.


402
00:37:08.930 --> 00:37:10.930
He doesn't know his own nature.
(sniffling)


403
00:37:11.810 --> 00:37:14.090
I suppose it's a sort
of innocence in him, really.


404
