429
00:38:35.850 --> 00:38:37.610
except this one
pathetic little frock.


430
00:38:38.210 --> 00:38:41.370
It was the one I painted her in.
God knows why I kept it.


431
00:38:42.730 --> 00:38:44.850
I pushed it out of sight
