649
01:00:17.570 --> 01:00:19.730
- Swine!!! Incredible swine!!!

650
01:00:19.850 --> 01:00:21.850
(grunting)
Let me get at him again!


651
01:00:23.850 --> 01:00:26.250
- You're right, you're right!
Oh, God. Oh, God.


652
01:00:27.690 --> 01:00:29.650
Leave me alone!
I'm done with you!


653
01:00:29.770 --> 01:00:31.770
- Oh, H.J., my dearest--
