695
01:03:52.850 --> 01:03:54.610
- In a hotel.

696
01:03:55.170 --> 01:03:58.610
What's it matter where I am?
I'm waiting for you.


697
01:03:58.730 --> 01:04:00.850
- And when I am free,
I'll have no money.


698
01:04:00.970 --> 01:04:02.090
I will have to leave France.

699
01:04:02.210 --> 01:04:03.770
You have friends
and you lose them.


700
01:04:03.890 --> 01:04:05.410
It's not so funny, you know!

701
01:04:05.530 --> 01:04:06.970
- Don't quarrel with me.

702
01:04:11.770 --> 01:04:14.090
- Forgive me. I'm, uh...

703
01:04:14.210 --> 01:04:16.050
