704
01:04:19.610 --> 01:04:21.650
Last Sunday,
when you didn't come--


705
01:04:21.770 --> 01:04:23.490
- No, don't.

706
01:04:23.610 --> 01:04:25.370
- You couldn't help it.
You were ll.


707
01:04:27.130 --> 01:04:28.170
- Yes.

708
01:04:28.850 --> 01:04:30.970
(metal rattling)
(French chatter)


709
01:04:35.330 --> 01:04:37.770
- Every number they called,
I thought it was mine.


710
01:04:38.010 --> 01:04:40.370
I was glad when the time was up,
I can tell you.


711
01:04:43.810 --> 01:04:45.970
You go mad, shut away in here.

712
01:04:47.290 --> 01:04:49.690
- I never will not turn up
again, Stephan.


713
01:04:50.850 --> 01:04:52.410
So don't worry.

714
01:05:08.330 --> 01:05:11.290
- I'm not late.
Your clock is fast.


715
01:05:14.330 --> 01:05:16.370
- What happened
the day before yesterday?


716
01:05:16.810 --> 01:05:17.890
And Saturday.

717
01:05:23.730 --> 01:05:25.050
One week.

718
01:05:25.610 --> 01:05:27.890
I haven't seen you for one week.

719
01:06:09.130 --> 01:06:11.050
- Open your eyes, savage.

720
01:06:13.610 --> 01:06:16.410
- I feel as if I'd fallen down
a precipice.


721
01:06:16.530 --> 01:06:17.970
(H.J. chuckling)

722
01:06:18.130 --> 01:06:19.690
- You funny thing.

723
01:06:20.690 --> 01:06:22.210
- Please.
- Hmm?


724
01:06:22.330 --> 01:06:23.570
- Be nice with me.

725
01:06:24.130 --> 01:06:25.530
I love you so.

726
01:06:25.970 --> 01:06:27.890
- There. There.

727
01:06:29.170 --> 01:06:31.450
There. You're such a darling...

728
01:06:32.810 --> 01:06:33.850
...pretty little thing.

729
01:06:34.370 --> 01:06:37.450
Such a funny,
pretty little thing.


730
01:06:40.810 --> 01:06:43.410
